source: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_SEQ_00<tab>The Budugan warrior squints at you.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_SEQ_00<tab>Le guerrier buduga a entendu des rumeurs à votre sujet.

source: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_000<tab>...Wait a minute. I know you. Your accomplishments are the only thing anyone talks about nowadays. If you are not too busy, might you agree to accompany me to the area below? There is something I want to show you.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_000<tab>Hé, c'est toi l'<var 08 E905 ((étrangère)) ((étranger)) /var> qui est <var 08 E905 ((revenue vivante)) ((revenu vivant)) /var> de la Force de Bardam<var 1D /var>? Tout le monde ne parle que de toi en ce moment... Suis-moi, j'ai quelque chose à te montrer.

source: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_001<tab>Hahaha! You need not look so skeptical. It is nothing too sinister, I assure you.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_001<tab>C-comment ça quoi<var 1D /var>? Suis-moi, tu verras bien<var 1D /var>! Où on va<var 1D /var>? Euh... en bas du Trône de l'Aube<var 1D /var>! Oui, c'est ça<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_002<tab>Even if it was, you are a hardened warrior, are you not? Now come, let us go before the day grows old.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_002<tab>Ce ne sera pas long<var 1D /var>! Allez, viens<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_010<tab><var 08 E905 ((She)) ((He)) /var>'s here! You can come out now, my friends!
target: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_010<tab>Oh, tu es là<var 1D /var>? Ha ha, c'est parfait<var 1D /var>! Hé, les gars, j'ai réussi à l'attirer<var 1D /var>! Ramenez vos fraises<var 1D /var>! (siffle)

source: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_020<tab>Bravo! That was quite a show! I am pleased to have been able to witness the extent of your strength firsthand. Even though these men had the element of surprise on their side, you defeated them with such ease!
target: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_020<tab>Bravo, c'était splendide<var 1D /var>! Tu es encore plus <var 08 E905 ((forte)) ((fort)) /var> que je l'imaginais. Déjouer une attaque surprise à trois contre <var 08 E905 ((une)) ((un)) /var> avec une telle aisance... Je suis soufflé<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_021<tab>But before that, please allow me to apologize for lying to you. Some of us wanted to test our strength against yours─the famed outsider who successfully followed in Bardam's footsteps─and I could think of no other way to bring you here.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_021<tab>Désolé, je t'ai menti. Je n'ai rien à te montrer... Hé, ne me regarde pas comme ça<var 1D /var>! Si je t'avais dit que je comptais t'attirer dans un traquenard pour évaluer tes capacités, aurais-tu accepté de me suivre<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_022<tab>It is now clear that your prowess on the battlefield is unparalleled. ...What would you say to joining us? Outsider or not, we would gladly welcome a man of your ability.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_022<tab>Bon, et sinon... tu n'as jamais songé à faire carrière chez les Buduga<var 1D /var>? Un guerrier de ta trempe, étranger ou pas, nous lui déroulerions le tapis rouge<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_023<tab><sigh> 'Tis a true shame you are a woman. Had you been a man, we would have gladly invited you to join our ranks. Were you Dotharl, we would even have awaited your reincarnation as a man. Alas, it seems our destinies were fated to diverge!
target: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_023<tab>Enfin bref... Rah, quel dommage que tu sois une femme... J'aurais aimé t'inviter à rejoindre les Buduga. Si encore tu étais dotharl, j'aurais pu attendre que tu te réincarnes en homme, mais là...

source: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_024<tab>Well, I suppose that is that. Anyroad, I would like to thank you for playing along. It was an enlightening experience. Now let us return to the Dawn Throne, shall we?
target: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_024<tab>Bah, tant pis... Merci d'avoir joué le jeu, en tout cas. Je rentre au Trône de l'Aube, on se retrouve là-haut<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_030<tab>The rumors─they do you no justice. You are possessed of the might of at least one hundred Budugan warriors.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_030<tab>Au cas où tu te poserais la question, oui, j'étais sérieux quand je parlais de faire de toi <var 08 E905 ((une)) ((un)) /var> Buduga. Tu es peut-être <var 08 E905 ((une étrangère)) ((un étranger)) /var> mais tu as la force de cent hommes. Le calcul est vite fait.

source: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_031<tab>Now I think on it, perhaps you are a little too strong to become one of us. Even if you somehow joined us, during training you would no doubt find yourself growing bored, for none of us would even come close to posing a challenge for you!
target: TEXT_STMBDZ526_02777_YOUNGFIGHTER02777_000_031<tab>Bon, voilà ce qu'on va faire<var 1D /var>: nous allons nous entraîner pour devenir aussi forts que toi, voire plus. Comme ça, ça te donnera envie de nous rejoindre<var 1D /var>!
